\begin_layout Section
Introduction
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\size larger
Wavy is a sensory substitution software package.
 Sensory substitution is defined by Wikipedia as :
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote

\size larger
[A process that mean] to transform the characteristics of one sensory modality
 into stimuli of another sensory modality.
 It is hoped that sensory substitution systems can help handicapped people
 by restoring their ability to perceive a certain defective sensory modality
 by using sensory information from a functioning sensory modality.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\size larger
For more details see :
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\size larger
\begin_inset Flex URL
